33
00:02:12.216 --> 00:02:13.675
Olav!

34
00:02:15.594 --> 00:02:18.055
What are we looking for?

35
00:02:18.430 --> 00:02:20.432
Just keep going.

36
00:02:21.099 --> 00:02:23.936
A little bit more or else we will be flagged on the site.

37
00:02:24.895 --> 00:02:26.897
Okay.
Continue the joke.

38
00:02:28.315 --> 00:02:32.152
The boy gets scared and leaves running from the room. crying.

39
00:02:32.736 --> 00:02:34.129
The mother says. "Honey!

40
00:02:34.155 --> 00:02:35.722
Now. what should we do? "

41
00:02:35.822 --> 00:02:37.199
You know women...

42
00:02:37.324 --> 00:02:40.953
The father says: "Let me handle this".

43
00:02:43.330 --> 00:02:45.415
Then he leaves and goes to the child's bedroom

44
00:02:45.541 --> 00:02:46.959
to say he was joking.

45
00:02:47.042 --> 00:02:48.877
He opens the door and sees the small bastard

46
00:02:48.961 --> 00:02:52.840
